item.title: Sorry Child, I’m Not Sorry
item.dc:creator: Sianokie
item.description:
Fortunately, or unfortunately, we don’t get to choose our family members. As we let out our first cry as babies, we are surrounded by people to whom we give the biological right and ability to make us shed heart-wrenching tears for the rest of our lives. Let’s say some family members explore this ability way...
